\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      The \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 agents, trained as both accountants and lawyers, were disgusted with Miss Trotter\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s laxity. She had not even photocopied the check from the Henry O\hich\f0 \rquote 
