\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      The twenty letters they collected with Miss Trotter\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s ledger included \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 
five that suggested the author had anticipated an official visit from investigators. The five were addressed to prominent religious leaders and were headed: \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Warning to the authorities!\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      They explained that the Madman was hooked to a \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 dead-man switch\'94\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0  that would automatically flood the world with more and different plagues should \'93
\loch\f0 \hich\f0 anyone interfere with me.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      Photocopies of all the letters from the Madman were among the first pieces of evidence studied at the Denver Isolation Center by The Team, as \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 they came to be known. The Team\hich\f0 \rquote 
\loch\f0 s first meeting came twenty-nine days after the Achill demonstration, a delay caused by political indecision in high places, an indecision which was put aside only after chilling developments worldwide.
