\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      Beckett\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 s expression remained bland and amiable. He said: \'93\loch\f0 The DIG may very well become the center of the world\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 s combined medical effort.\'94

\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 But first we prove ourselves, eh?\'94\loch\f0  Hupp asked.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 First we t\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 ry to understand our enemy \hich\f0 \endash \loch\f0 \hich\f0  the man and not the plague,\'94\loch\f0  Beckett said.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Where was this decision made?\'94\loch\f0  Godelinsky asked.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 At the highest levels,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Beckett said. \'93\loch\f0 Most of the other groups, so I\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 m told, are also working in this way as well as on th
\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 e question of how he spread his plague. That is the highest priority. Can we cut him off and go after him openly on all fronts?\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Tomorrow, we start the medical work, hein?\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Danzas demanded. \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 When the technicians come?\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 That, too,\'94\loch\f0  Beckett said.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Too!\'94\loch\f0  Foss said.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 I have received no such orders,\'94\loch\f0  Lepikov said.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 There\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 s a telephone in your room,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Beckett said. \'93\loch\f0 You\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 re free to use it.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 And who will listen?\'94\loch\f0  Lepikov demanded.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Our secret police and yours,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Beckett said. \'93\loch\f0 Wh\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 o cares? Call your boss and get your orders.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Secrecy is our only hope,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Godelinsky said. \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 If he is insane, we cannot predict him.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 Who doubts he\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 s insane?\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Foss asked. \'93\loch\f0 He\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 s driven the whole world nuts. Including the politicians!
\'94
