\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 We are to conce\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 ntrate on how he spread the disease,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Beckett said. \'93\loch\f0 They still haven\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 
t solved it.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      It was The Team\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s third afternoon and they had moved their meeting to the small dining room off the DIC\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s main cafeteria. It was closer to the lab facilities, had brig
\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 
hter walls and lighting, a smaller table. Coffee or tea could be delivered via a pass-through with a sliding panel from the kitchen. Security had objected and there was a certain amount of crockery clatter to contend with, but it was a more comfortable se
\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 t\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 ting for all of them.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Is anyone asking does our Madman act alone?\'94\loch\f0  Hupp asked. He moved aside slightly as a white-aproned waiter finished clearing away the dishes from their lunch.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 A conspiracy?\'94\loch\f0  Lepikov asked. He looked at the departing waiter\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 . \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Are those waiters in your army, Bill?\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      Foss answered: \'93\loch\f0 It\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s our most carefully guarded secret, Sergei. Two years of this duty and they\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 re guaranteed to be insane killers.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      Even Lepikov joined in the wry chuckle at Foss\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s wit.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      Danzas said:\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0  \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Infected birds. We have the precedent of parrot fever. Could he have modified psittacosis?\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 Somehow that doesn\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 t strike me as his style,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Hupp said. \'93\loch\f0 He\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 
s not leaving us an easy trail to follow. No.\'94\loch\f0  He looked down at a blue folder in front of him,\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0  opened it slowly and leafed through the enclosed pages until he found what he was seeking. \'93\loch\f0 There
\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 s this from his second letter,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Hupp said. \'93\loch\f0 I know there are links between the IRA and the Fedayeen, links with Japanese terrorists, the Tupamaros and God k\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 n
\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 ows who else. I was tempted to spread my revenge into all the lands that have harbored such cowards. I warn those lands: do not tempt me again for I have released only a small part of my arsenal.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      Hupp closed the folder and looked up at Lepikov across\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0  the table from him. \'93\loch\f0 
We must assume that this is not an empty threat. I do not think this man bluffs. On that assumption, we must also assume that he has more than one way to spread his arsenal. Because if we find the way or ways he did it in the present
\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0  \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 instance, we could close off that channel.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Could we?\'94\loch\f0  Beckett asked.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      Lepikov nodded to agree that he shared this doubt.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      Godelinsky leaned forward, sipped her tea, then: \'93\loch\f0 He infected specific areas. The fact that his plague has spread, this\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 
 can only mean human carriers are involved in some way.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Why is that?\'94\loch\f0  Danzas asked.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 The way everything is being sprayed, no insect could be doing it,\'94\loch\f0  she said. Godelinsky rubbed her forehead and frowned.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      Lepikov said something to her, lo\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 w-voiced, in Russian. Foss caught only part of it, but turned to peer sharply at the other woman.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Is something amiss?\'94\loch\f0  Hupp asked.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Only a headache,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Godelinsky said. \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 I think it is the water change. Perhaps I could have some more tea?\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      Bec\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 kett turned to the panel behind him, opened it and confronted a face bent close on the other side, a bland, smiling blond man with white teeth. \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 
Anyone else want something from the kitchen?\'94\loch\f0  the man asked.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Bumpkins!\'94\loch\f0  Lepikov said.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 They just hav\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 en\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 t had time to install microphones in this room,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Foss said. \'93\loch\f0 It\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 
ll be less obtrusive tomorrow. I\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 ll take coffee, black.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      Beckett glanced around the table. The others demurred. He returned his attention to the bland face at the pass-through. \'93\loch\f0 You he\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 ard?\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Right-O, Doc.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      The covering panel slid closed.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      Beckett returned his attention to the table.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      Hupp lifted a briefcase from the floor beside his chair, wiped a piece of lettuce from it, and removed a small notepad and pen. \'93\loch\f0 It will \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 be something simple,\'94
\loch\f0  he said.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      The panel behind Beckett slid open. \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 One tea, one coffee, black.\'94\loch\f0  It was Bland Face. He pushed two steaming cups onto the inner ledge, closed the panel.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      Without getting up, Beckett took the two cups from the ledge a\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 
nd slid them along the table. As Godelinsky took her cup, Beckett noted a patch of white on the back of her left hand. It was not prominent, but quite noticeable to his trained eye. Before he could comment on it, Lepikov said:
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 I think the plague was \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 spread with some devilish American device. A spray can for the hair, possibly.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      Hupp wrote on his notepad. \'93\loch\f0 It\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s on my list, but I doubt it. Again, it\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 s too obvious a thing for our Madman.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      Godelinsky sipped noisily at her tea, then: \'93\loch\f0 I agree wit\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 h Joe. It is not O\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 Neill\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 s style.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 What is her style?\'94\loch\f0  Foss asked.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      Hupp smiled at the cautionary change of gender. \'93\loch\f0 As I said, I think it will be something remarkably simple. It will be a thing of which we will say: \hich\f0 \lquote \loch\f0 Oh, my God! Of course!
\hich\f0 \rquote \'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0    \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0   \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Such as?\'94\loch\f0  Beckett prompted.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      Hupp produced a high-shouldered shrug, palms thrust out and upward. \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 I address only the question of style, not the specific method.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 We don\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 t know the incubation period,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Godelinsky said. \'93\loch\f0 This could\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 ve been sittin
\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 g there for months.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Contaminated gifts?\'94\loch\f0  Foss asked.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 That kind of thing,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Hupp said. \'93\loch\f0 A toy that a mother would handle before passing it along to her child. We must not forget that O\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 
Neill\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s wife and children were slain. He speaks of appropria\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 te revenge.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Diabolical,\'94\loch\f0  Danzas muttered.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Insane,\'94\loch\f0  Lepikov said.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Indeed,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Hupp agreed. \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 It is the madness in his method that will open the door to him.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      Godelinsky drained her teacup, put it down and stared down the table at Foss. \'93\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Tell me, Ari, if you are this Madwoman, how is it you do this thing?\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 In some common food item, perhaps?\'94\loch\f0  Foss said.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Potatoes?\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Lepikov asked. \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 That is too droll.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      Hupp raised a monitory finger. \'93\loch\f0 Ahhh, but she has touched the essence. It m\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 
ust be a common thing. It must be something used in Ireland, Britain and Libya, and it must be a thing that exposes the maximum number of women to contamination.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Why women?\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Beckett asked. \'93\loch\f0 Why can\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 t men be the carriers?\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      Danzas, following his \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 usual pattern of not contributing to a Team exchange until it was well along, said: \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 
There is another quality required by the limitations we can assume are imposed on our Madman.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      Attention turned toward him.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 How does he gain access to the distr\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 ibution system?\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Danzas asked. \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 
I agree that it must be something simple and common to the three regions, but it also must be available to the Madman, and probably without elaborate preparation or a complicated conspiracy.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 He\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 s a loner,\'94\loch\f0  Beckett sai\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 d.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 A devious intelligence,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Lepikov said. \'93\loch\f0 The scientific abilities he demonstrates in the laboratory will, I\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 
m sure, apply to his distribution method.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Devious, yes,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Hupp said, \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 but not necessarily based in scientific complexity. His style\'85\loch\f0  i\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 
t is more likely to be a very common item he contaminates, perhaps something each of us carries on his person at this very moment.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      Silence greeted Hupp\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s suggestion.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      Beckett nodded, more to himself than to Hupp. There was the ring of truth about\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0  this suggestion. It was O\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 Neill\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 
s style. Simplicity, that was the keynote.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Why could it not be a conspiracy?\'94\loch\f0  Lepikov asked.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      Godelinsky shook her head.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Insects?\'94\loch\f0  Foss asked.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 An insect vector of the plague,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Lepikov said. \'93\loch\f0 Would that\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0  not fit your description, Joe?\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 But how would he distribute them?\'94\loch\f0  Hupp asked.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 The eggs or the larvae?\'94\loch\f0  Foss asked.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Again, the distribution is the question,\'94\loch\f0  Hupp said.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Air travel makes such a concept the nemesis of our world,\'94\loch\f0  Lep\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 ikov said.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 What about contamination of the water systems in the target regions?\'94\loch\f0  Danzas asked.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Insects in the water?\'94\loch\f0  Lepikov asked.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Or the disease itself,\'94\loch\f0  Danzas said.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      Hupp pounded a fist gently on the table. \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Distribution,\'94\loch\f0  he sai\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 d. \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 How?\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Just a minute,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Foss said. \'93\loch\f0 Insects in the water \hich\f0 \endash \loch\f0  that\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 
s not a bad idea. Whaling captains deliberately spread mosquito larvae all through the South Pacific as revenge against native societies that offended them in some way.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 Then per\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 haps an airline attendant or a pilot,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Lepikov said. \'93\loch\f0 Is this O\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 Neill a pilot?\'94

\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Negative,\'94\loch\f0  Beckett said.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 But the involvement of air travel in this thing,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Lepikov said. \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 That idea has its appeal.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      Beckett said: \'93\loch\f0 Hawaii gets fifty new insec\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 ts a year thanks to air travel.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 What is carried universally by such aircraft?\'94\loch\f0  Lepikov asked.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Luggage, packages,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Beckett said. \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 The tourists themselves, but\'85\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  He shook his head. \'93\loch\f0 
This ignores the fact that he pinpoints his targets \hich\f0 \endash \loch\f0  Ireland, \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Britain and Libya.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 With no guarantee that others escape,\'94\loch\f0  Foss said.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      Godelinsky rubbed at her forehead. \'93\loch\f0 And we cannot be sure that he uses only one method. Incubation period \hich\f0 \endash \loch\f0 \hich\f0  that is essential to our considerations.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 The mails,\'94\loch\f0  Hupp sa\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 id.
