\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      In the sudden silence, Beckett removed his hand from Foss\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s neck. Tears were running down his cheeks.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Damn him! Damn him!\'94\loch\f0  Beck\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 ett muttered.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 They\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 re arranging for us to do the autopsies in the OR,\'94\loch\f0  Danzas said.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Oh, fuck off, you bloody French prig!\'94\loch\f0  Beckett shouted.
