\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Donnell said. \'93\loch\f0 There\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s a kind of poetry in it, you going out there to see if it\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s really him. You\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 ve a special motivation.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 I\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 m told you know that country above Youghal,\'94\loch\f0  Doheny said.
