\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 n\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0  by the hearth-side stories in the night \hich\f0 \endash \loch\f0  of tyrant cruelties and the agonies of ancestors. The shuddering realities of Ireland\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 
