     It was midafternoon and they were plodding upward out of another shallow valley, the boy and the priest walking a bit ahead. The boy had been even more withdrawn since the fight in the bath house, his silence a deeper thing. Father Michae
\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 l was accusatory. It was all Herity\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s fault.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      It\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s all that damned Yank\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s fault!
