ne gun was still cradled against his breast. He took a moment to catch his breath, then: \'93\loch\f0 There\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s two cottages just over the next ridge and smoke from the both of them. There\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 
