\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 
e left. There was a smell of cow manure from it. The valley beyond contained a scattering of burned-out cottages and wrecked outbuildings, not a sign of smoke there. He returned his attention to the near cottage. A clothesline had been strung from a corne
\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 r\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0  of the building to a post in the stone-enclosed yard. Clothing waved in the wind there \hich\f0 \endash \loch\f0 \hich\f0  trousers, shirts, long underwear\'85\loch\f0 \hich\f0 
