behind the sound of the radio and the clucking of the chickens.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      Abruptly, John froze at the sound of voices almost directly below him under the rock outcropping where he could not see.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 They\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 ll not see us in here.\'94\loch\f0  It was the voice of a young boy\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 .
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 How much in the bottle?\'94\loch\f0  Another young voice.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Almost a cup.\'94\loch\f0  That was the first one.
