in which he thought he could hear his own heart beating too loudly. He dared not move. He might scrape against the rock, alerting the boys, and they could call a warning to the people in the cottages. He moved only his eyes, trying to glimpse Herity, wond
\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 e\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 ring where the man might be.
