\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Should we answer?\'94\loch\f0  That was the second child.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 No! Stay here. If it\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s trouble we\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 ll be safer in here.\'94
