\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 A stranger, so they say. But he w\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 as killed with a shotgun.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 And they can\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 t explain that rifle shot we heard,\'94\loch\f0  John said.
