\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 You listen when the professor talks!\'94\loch\f0  Murphey bridled.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      It was then that Gannon first revealed his Trinity College background.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 I knew I\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 d seen you someplace,\'94\loch\f0  Father Mich\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 ael said.
