\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      Herity sat back, smiling. \'93\loch\f0 Then would you tell us, Perfesser, what\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 s beyond apathy?\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 The women are gone forever,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Gannon said, his voice heavy. \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 The women are gone and nothing\'85\loch\f0  nothing! will bri\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 
