\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 And wise men like Mister O\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 Donnell here will find a cure for the plague,\'94\loch\f0  Murp\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 hey said. \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 
Things will come back to an even keel, Professor. Depend on it.\'94
