\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 That we are moving inexorably toward an edge where we\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 ll drop off into nothing. What\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s beyond apathy? This thing some of you think of as life 
\hich\f0 \endash \loch\f0 \hich\f0  this is already death.\'94
