\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Living!\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Herity said. \'93\loch\f0 Now, didn\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 t you hear the perfesser? This is not living.\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  He lifted his glass. 
