\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 To bloody Ireland!\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Herity said, raising his glass high. \'93\loch\f0 May she rise up from the dead and smite down the devil who injured us! And may he suffer a thousand 
