\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 Out to the byre, it being full of soft straw? Out there to dream of rolling in\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0  the straw with a young woman of your choice?\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Leave him alone,\'94\loch\f0  Murphey said, his voice mild.
