\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      Feeling oddly displaced, John went to sleep that night in an upper bedroom of Gannon\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 
 cottage, clean sheets and a lumpy mattress. He had one short stub of a candle to light him to the room, which smelled of soap and some flowery perfume. There was a single wooden chair, a low dresser and a standing wardrobe that reminded him of the one in
\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0  \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 the Hotel Normandy.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      O\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 Neill-Within had become quiescent, moving deeper, more remote and\'85\loch\f0  John felt it: satisfied.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      He had seen what he had seen.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      While preparing for bed, John thought about the drinking session at the supper table. It had resu\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 med in the kitchen after the herb tea in the parlor \hich\f0 \endash \loch\f0 
