 Little Tim has built a hut beside his wife\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s grave at Glasnevin and that\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 s where he sleeps now.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Murphey cleared his throat, his attention on the empty jug that Gannon was removing to the sink. \'93\loch\f0 We\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 ll solve it, by God! I know we will!
\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  He cast a bleary glance around the table. \'93\loch\f0 Where\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 s my Kenneth?\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Gone to bed,\'94\loch\f0  Gannon said.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 I\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 ll yet dandl\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 e me grandson on me knee,\'94\loch\f0  Murphey said.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Everyone clings to a dream such as that,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Gannon said, leaning against the drainboard. \'93\loch\f0 Until something overwhelms them. It\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 
s the dream of personal survival \hich\f0 \endash \loch\f0  a victory over Time. Some submit to religion or ma\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 ke a daring assault on \hich\f0 \lquote \loch\f0 the secrets of the universe,\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 
 or live in hope of genie-chance. It\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 s all the same thing.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      John could visualize Gannon standing in front of a classroom delivering those portentous phrases, and in that same pedantic tone. Gannon h\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 
ad said that same thing many times and in those same words.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      Murphey looked admiringly at his brother-in-law. \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 The wisdom in that man!\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      Herity chuckled. \'93\loch\f0 You know what the Yanks call your perfesser\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s \hich\f0 \lquote \loch\f0 genie-chance\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 ? They call it\'85\loch\f0 
 they call it the \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 blond in the Cadillac automobile!\'94\loch\f0  Laughter set his hand trembling, spilling some of the poteen from his glass.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 It has other variations,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Gannon said. \'93\loch\f0 The magic number, the winning ticket on the Sweeps, the treasure that you stumble upon in your own
