\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      Gannon smiled sadly. \'93\loch\f0 I think I\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 ll go down to the graves. Where did you leave the lantern, Wick?\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 On the back stoop.\'94
