\'85\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 And sure and we all know there\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s witches, don\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 t we, Father Michael?\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Herity peered at the priest with owlish glee. \'93
\loch\f0 \hich\f0 And the faeries, now! What about them?\'94
