\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 The first room to the right at the top of the stairs, Father,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Gannon said. \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Sleep with the angels, God willing.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      Gannon turned and let himself out the kitchen door.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      On impulse, John followed, finding \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 Gannon there lighting a slender lantern with a kitchen match. Clouds covered the sky and there was a feeling of mist in the air.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 Tell me, Mister O\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 Donnell, are you accompanying me because you fear I have other weapons hidden out here?\'94
