\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 A soldier, that one,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Gannon said. \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 A Provo or I miss my guess. I know the type.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      John felt an abrupt emptiness in his stomach. Herity\'85\loch\f0  one of the Provisional IRA. There was the so\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 und of truth in Gannon\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 
