\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 I was speaking of the two-legged kind,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Herity said. He drained his glass. Standing slowly, deliberately, Herity said: \'93\loch\f0 
