\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      He hurried to dress, hearing the sounds of people moving downstairs, smelling lard heating\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0  in a pan. The odor of the tea herb mingled with peat smoke.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      Breakfast was a silent time \hich\f0 \endash \loch\f0  boiled eggs and soda bread. Murphey appeared bright-eyed, showing no effects of the night\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 
