\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      Through me, John thought.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      Had O\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 Neill imagined such a scene as this?
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      There was no memory of su\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 ch a thing, no inner movie to recount it. Cold I was when I did the thing. Cold and murderous \hich\f0 \endash \loch\f0  not caring who I hurt.
