\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      This brought an appreciative chuckle.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      Velcourt could see Shiloh debating whether to address the Presiden\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 t as Sam. All of that diplomatic training won out.
