re saying that we have our people over there, too. However, I was addressing a different situation. The Soviets and the United States are now confined to leopard spots of plague-free communities. A comparison of the relati\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 v
\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 e vulnerability of these population centers shows us clearly at the advantage.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Is that so?\'94
