re already \hich\f0 \endash \'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Shiloh! The Soviet Union will follow its own best interests. As will we. The premier is a pragmatist.\'94
