\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 You have a good memory, sir, but the Commun\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 ists mean to do us in. We can\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 t afford to relax for a\'85\'94
