re cooperating well in the search for some way of preventi\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 ng human extinction.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 And what if they\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 re first to find a cure?\'94
