\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 o Beckett myself last week before\'85\loch\f0  Well, we\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 re communicating. Of course, each of us listens to these communications. I don\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 
t suppose this will lead to the millennium but it is one hopeful sign in a world beset by the threat of extinction. And if there\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s a\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 n\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 
 advantage to be gained, Shiloh, from this cooperation, an advantage gained without compromising our mutual efforts, I will take that advantage.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 With all due respect, sir, are you assuming they don\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 t have research facilities that are kept completely\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0  secret from us?\'94
