\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 Mister President, I presume on past association. We go a long way back where \hich\f0 \endash \'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 Where I was often right and you were w\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 rong.\'94
