\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      Broderick gripped the arms of his chair, knuckles white. His voice came out in barely controlled fury: \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Sir, the intelligent ones must lead!\'94
