\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      Herity and Liam Cullen stood in a clearing below the sheep-grazed meado\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 wland that fronted Brann McCrae\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 
s great house, aware that they were watched by John about a hundred meters above. The two men appeared to be admiring the dusk as it crept down the hills toward the valley and the chateau. Swallows dived after insects in th\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 e
