\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Except for McCrae up there,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Liam said, \'93\loch\f0 it\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s not a one of us can say he\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 ll live in
