\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 Ahhh, don\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 t say it, Liam.\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  That was Jock speaking from behind John. \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 
Those sweet darlings just up there and us outside never to touch.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 This is what we get for living only with our hatreds,\'94\loch\f0  Father M\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 ichael muttered. \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 
We must stop the hatreds, Joseph! We must save that sinner up there!\'94
