\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Evil!\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Liam,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Herity said, \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 you and Jock are such great companions. So helpful.\'94
