Was you really just trying to get away, John?\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 That was a stupid thing to do, putting us all in that hut,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  John said. \'93\loch\f0 That\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 s a crazy man up there. He could do anything.
