\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      Velcourt recognized none of these na\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 mes, but he heard the awe in Ruckerman\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s voice. There was also something on which a politician could focus.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 You have a publication that he used?\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Just one. He had loaned it to a student and the student forgot to return it.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 This O\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 Neill s\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 ounds like a complete laboratory team all in one man,\'94\loch\f0  Velcourt said.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 He was multi-talented, no doubt of that,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Saddler agreed. \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Had to be to crack that code all by himself.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      Ruckerman said: \'93\loch\f0 The psychological profile suggests that some of his t\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 
alents may have lain dormant until released by the driving passion ignited when his family was killed.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      Saddler said: \'93\loch\f0 Milton Dressier is now insisting that O\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 Neill was at least a latent schizoid and was driven into this genius mode by access to a dif\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 
\hich\f0 ferent personality that lay dormant until that bombing in Ireland.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      Velcourt had heard of Dressier \hich\f0 \endash \loch\f0 \hich\f0  the psychoanalyst in charge of the Profile Team. The President said: \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 
He went nuts, and the nut was the one who was capable of doing this.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 In a\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0  nutshell,\'94\loch\f0  Saddler said.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      All three of them joined in a nervous laugh. Saddler and the President stared at each other afterward, abashed.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      Velcourt had little time to review the briefing after the men left. Something they said, though, nagged at h\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 im. Something about breaking a code.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      As the day\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s fatigue threatened to overwhelm him, he tried to recapture that elusive something. It was full dark outside by now and the lights of the Capitol bright against a cloudy sky.
