\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      The boy sat down on the floor besi\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 de the fire and extended his hands toward the warmth. Herity put his pack next to John\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 
s beside the door, glanced at the machine gun propped against it and smiled. He looked around the room: no loft, only this one small enclosed space.
