\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      She played it now in the morning quiet of their confinement, her eyes closed, her feet tucked under her on the chair. Stephen could be heard where he sat across from her, the pages of his book \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 
