 a bone polished by our own teeth! And no meat left on it at all. In the end, we throw it away for the useless thing it is\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 .\loch\af0\dbch\af11\hich\f0 \'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      John\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 s lips once more formed the words: \'93\loch\f0 What\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 s happening?\'94\loch\f0  There was no voice behind it.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      Doheny cocked an ear toward the door. There was a faint slamming sound in the distance. He said: \'93\loch\f0 The truth is, we Irish, preferring to make epics out of \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 
disasters, could find no victory to serve the same function. We may say otherwise, but our actions give the truth to my words. We prefer disasters.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      John backed away from Doheny, stopped by the side of the cot. His knees trembled.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 You\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 re going t\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 o be put on trial, John,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Doheny said. \'93\loch\f0 And they\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 
ll have me along afterwards to stand in their dock.\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  He grinned. \'93\loch\f0 Because I\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 ve denied to Kevin the real prize he sought here \hich\f0 \endash \loch\f0 \hich\f0  little Katie Browder!\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      Feet could be heard running in the hallway.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 Li\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 sten to me, John!\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Doheny said. \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 You must demand Father Michael for your defense counsel.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      John found a hoarse whisper with which to speak. \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Defend me from what?\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Promise me, you fool!\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      John\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s head nodded agreement on its own.
