 only stop. Darkness made it worse. And the wild noises outside. The sourness arose once more in her throat. Abruptly, with barely time for her to put her head out of the blanket shelter and turn away from the baby and Stephen, she vomited. The smell perm
\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 e\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 ated the chamber.
