\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      Slim \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 and Baldy kept firm grips on his upper arms as they hurried him across the courtyard into the administration wing, then down a yellow corridor and up the stairs to the castle library.

\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      Every light in the library had been turned on. The crystal chandeli\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 
ers danced with brilliants. Spotlight sconces focused on a raised platform that had been built near the fireplace out of plywood nailed to heavy timbers. A trestle table had been placed on the plywood and leather armchairs set up behind it. Kevin O
\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 Donnel\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 l\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 
