\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 I have in my hand a bit of the roof timber from Cashell. It is a token that Irish Law prevails \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 here.\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0 
