\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 He does not want to hear,\'94\loch\f0  Doheny said. He turned back to the jury with what he hoped was a look of sincerity. This was not a plea\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 
