\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      The jurors chuckled.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      Doheny thought then about the points he and Herity and O\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 Donnell had gone over before assembling here. Had he touched them all? Insanity\'85\loch\f0 \hich\f0  reason\'85\loch\f0 
