\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 But I was only trying to silence O\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 Neill\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 s screaming,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  John said. Father Michael leaped to his feet. \'93\loch\f0 
