\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      Silence settled over the room.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      Father Michael sighed. He turned and looked at the jurors. What was the sense talking to more death\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s-heads? he wondered. Might just as well address Alex\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 
