\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 There is a pattern here,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Father Michael said. \'93\loch\f0 A clear pattern woven inextricably into other patterns \hich\f0 \endash \loch\f0 
