\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Ignore this pattern and we slay this world finally with ignorance. Recognize it and our values change. We will know then what to preserve.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      Father Michael fell silent for a moment and glanced back at the boy, who stood staring at him with a look of wo\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 
nder. Could that young lad understand? Was this the only mind in the room worth addressing?
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      Doheny felt himself deeply moved by the priest\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s words. God! The man was an Irish orator from the old tradition. The jurymen were obviously disturbed by him. T\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 
