\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      The door behind Doheny burst open with a crash. A uniformed member of Kevin\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 s guard came rushing across the room. \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Sir!\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0 
