\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      Wycombe-Finch stooped to peer at the new weld under the chamber, then straightened. \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 It must be hellish in there,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  he said. \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 
