\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 I\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 ve told \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 them we\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 re working as fast as we can to produce enough for the mother and baby.\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0 
