\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 It works in the test tube.\'94\loch\f0  He shrugged.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 I see. Well, if it doesn\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 t perform outside the glassworks, Stoney will be rather put out.\loch\af0\dbch\af11\hich\f0 \'94
