\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 You Americans! You\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 re so gross under pressure. I believe that\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s why you\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 \hich\f0 
ve produced so few really good administrators.\'94
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      Beckett clamped his mouth shut to suppress an angry reply. Abruptly, he strode away from the director, \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 
