\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      Wycombe-Finch touched Beckett\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s shoulder then\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 , shocking him because the construction noise had concealed the man\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s approach.
