\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      Poor Hupp. His dreams of \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 being a power broker dispensing the scientific largesse with a careful hand \hich\f0 \endash \loch\f0  all gone. A cruel awakening into this new civilization.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 We are cows,\'94\loch\f0  Hupp had said.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0      This had brought shocked silence to the other members of The Team, all four of the\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 m holding their last meeting, parting finally in the impersonal crockery, tile and chromium of Huddersfield
\hich\f0 \rquote \loch\f0 s main cafeteria. There had been much noisy activity out beyond their corner table. Huddersfield had become a world crossroads, every facility over\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 l\hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 oaded.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 Joe is upset because our old team is breaking up,\'94\loch\f0  Lepikov explained.
