\par \hich\af0\dbch\af11\loch\f0 \hich\f0      \'93\loch\f0 \hich\f0 You were not raised on the land as we were, Sergei,\'94\loch\f0 \hich\f0  Hupp said. \'93\loch\f0 You would not understand about poor, dumb cows. You never walk up to
